# Disclaimer & Guidelines Compliance

* Stellive Fan-Content Guidelines Compliance
  - StelLane strictly adheres to the Stellive Fan-Content Guidelines (https://cafe.naver.com/f-e/cafes/29424353/articles/709417).
  - "This game is a Stellive fan creation (fan game). It is not an official product of Stellive, and there is no official relationship or affiliation with Stellive, other than the background context of the game's development."

* Limitation of Liability
  - Any and all legal liabilities, consequences, or damages resulting from the redistribution, modification, sale, or commercial misuse of this game rest entirely with the user who performs such actions.
  - StelLane and its original developers assume no responsibility or liability for any issues (including but not limited to copyright disputes, system malfunctions, or legal penalties) arising from the use, modification, distribution, or commercial exploitation of this software.

